  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 4059.9999999999995,
      "end_time": 5040.0,
      "text": "You see this little gadget?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 6100.0,
      "end_time": 7800.0,
      "text": "Let's call it an \"iEverything.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8760.0,
      "end_time": 9480.0,
      "text": "You can't get it yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9480.0,
      "end_time": 12300.0,
      "text": "but if technology keeps moving as fast as it is now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12700.0,
      "end_time": 14840.0,
      "text": "the iEverything will be with us before you know it;"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14840.0,
      "end_time": 16920.0,
      "text": "a combination of intelligent computing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 17200.0,
      "end_time": 18340.0,
      "text": "3D manufacturing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 18540.0,
      "end_time": 19900.0,
      "text": "big data crunching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19900.0,
      "end_time": 21720.0,
      "text": "and advanced biotechnology."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 22060.0,
      "end_time": 23240.0,
      "text": "This little machine will be able"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 23240.0,
      "end_time": 24920.0,
      "text": "to do everything you want"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24920.0,
      "end_time": 26820.0,
      "text": "and give you everything you need."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 28000.0,
      "end_time": 28900.0,
      "text": "There's only one hitch."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 29680.0,
      "end_time": 31140.0,
      "text": "As the economy is now organized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 31280.0,
      "end_time": 32820.0,
      "text": "no one will be able to buy it"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 33200.0,
      "end_time": 35580.0,
      "text": "because there won't be any paying jobs left."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 36440.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "You see, the iEverything will do..."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 39240.0,
      "end_time": 39880.0,
      "text": "everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 41280.0,
      "end_time": 42520.0,
      "text": "I'm exaggerating a bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 42520.0,
      "end_time": 43860.0,
      "text": "in order to make a point about"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 43860.0,
      "end_time": 45900.0,
      "text": "the trend we're already seeing."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 46220.0,
      "end_time": 48540.0,
      "text": "Even now, we're producing more and more"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 48540.0,
      "end_time": 50240.0,
      "text": "with fewer and fewer people."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 50340.0,
      "end_time": 51700.0,
      "text": "Internet sales are on the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 51700.0,
      "end_time": 54220.0,
      "text": "to replacing millions of retail workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 54480.0,
      "end_time": 56680.0,
      "text": "Diagnostic apps will be replacing"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 56680.0,
      "end_time": 59500.0,
      "text": "hundreds of thousands of healthcare workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 59660.0,
      "end_time": 61560.0,
      "text": "Self-driving cars and trucks"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 61740.0,
      "end_time": 64140.0,
      "text": "will replace five million drivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 64140.0,
      "end_time": 65560.0,
      "text": "*digital voice* Where would you like to go?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 66160.0,
      "end_time": 68360.0,
      "text": "Researchers estimate that almost half"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 68580.0,
      "end_time": 70760.0,
      "text": "of all U.S. jobs are at risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 70760.0,
      "end_time": 73440.0,
      "text": "of being automated in the next two decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 73700.0,
      "end_time": 75280.0,
      "text": "Now, this isn't necessarily bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 75520.0,
      "end_time": 76840.0,
      "text": "The economy we're heading toward"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 76840.0,
      "end_time": 79740.0,
      "text": "could offer millions of people more free time"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 79860.0,
      "end_time": 81400.0,
      "text": "to do what they want"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 81600.0,
      "end_time": 83600.0,
      "text": "instead of what they have to do to earn a living."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 84420.0,
      "end_time": 85680.0,
      "text": "But, to make this work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 85680.0,
      "end_time": 88800.0,
      "text": "we'll have to figure out some way to recirculate the money"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 89020.0,
      "end_time": 90880.0,
      "text": "from the relatively few people"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 91060.0,
      "end_time": 93940.0,
      "text": "who do very well in the economy of the iEverything"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 93940.0,
      "end_time": 96340.0,
      "text": "to the rest of us, who will want to buy"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 96540.0,
      "end_time": 97680.0,
      "text": "the iEverythings."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 98480.0,
      "end_time": 99740.0,
      "text": "One possible answer:"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 99740.0,
      "end_time": 102100.0,
      "text": "a universal basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 103580.0,
      "end_time": 104840.0,
      "text": "possibly financed out of"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 104840.0,
      "end_time": 107220.0,
      "text": "the profits going to labor-replacing innovations."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 107740.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "The idea of a universal basic income historically"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112700.0,
      "text": "has had support from people on both the left"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 117800.0,
      "end_time": 118540.0,
      "text": "and the right."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 123840.0,
      "end_time": 125980.0,
      "text": "In the 1970's, President Nixon"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 125980.0,
      "end_time": 128400.0,
      "text": "proposed a similar concept for the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 128400.0,
      "end_time": 130300.0,
      "text": "and it even passed the House of Representatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 130520.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132080.0,
      "text": "*President Nixon* I therefore propose"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 135420.0,
      "text": "that we abolish the present welfare system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 135420.0,
      "end_time": 138460.0,
      "text": "and a basic federal minimum would be provided."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 138980.0,
      "end_time": 141820.0,
      "text": "The idea is getting some traction again."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 142400.0,
      "end_time": 144740.0,
      "text": "Some think it could be superior to welfare"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 144900.0,
      "end_time": 146300.0,
      "text": "or other kinds of public assistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 146300.0,
      "end_time": 148580.0,
      "text": "because a universal basic income doesn't"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 148700.0,
      "end_time": 151200.0,
      "text": "tell people what to spend the assistance on."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 151420.0,
      "end_time": 152680.0,
      "text": "And everyone qualifies."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 153400.0,
      "end_time": 155220.0,
      "text": "In recent years, evidence has shown that"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 155220.0,
      "end_time": 156860.0,
      "text": "giving people cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 156860.0,
      "end_time": 158360.0,
      "text": "as a way to address poverty"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 158360.0,
      "end_time": 159440.0,
      "text": "actually works."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 159700.0,
      "end_time": 161620.0,
      "text": "In study after study, people"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 161620.0,
      "end_time": 163900.0,
      "text": "don't stop working, and they don't drink it away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 163900.0,
      "end_time": 165120.0,
      "text": "they actually use it"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 165120.0,
      "end_time": 166900.0,
      "text": "to increase their earnings."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 168100.0,
      "end_time": 170480.0,
      "text": "Interest in a basic income is surging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 170800.0,
      "end_time": 172860.0,
      "text": "with governments debating it from Finland,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 172860.0,
      "end_time": 173700.0,
      "text": "to Canada,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 173800.0,
      "end_time": 174800.0,
      "text": "to Namibia."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 175140.0,
      "end_time": 177180.0,
      "text": "The charity Give Directly"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 177400.0,
      "end_time": 180180.0,
      "text": "is about to launch a basic income pilot in Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 180500.0,
      "end_time": 183020.0,
      "text": "Providing an income for more than ten years"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 183200.0,
      "end_time": 185900.0,
      "text": "to some of the poorest and most vulnerable families"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 186020.0,
      "end_time": 187320.0,
      "text": "on the planet, and then"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 187320.0,
      "end_time": 189300.0,
      "text": "rigorously evaluate the results."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 190360.0,
      "end_time": 192240.0,
      "text": "As new technologies replace work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 192240.0,
      "end_time": 193620.0,
      "text": "the question for the future is"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 193620.0,
      "end_time": 196480.0,
      "text": "how best to provide economic security for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 196960.0,
      "end_time": 199340.0,
      "text": "A universal basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 199780.0,
      "end_time": 201580.0,
      "text": "could be an answer."
    }
  ]
}